      "desc": "If this unit has [FaubismMaskMeursault], inflict +1 more [BearClawWoundAlly]\n\nEvery time this unit inflicts 4 [BearClawWoundAlly], heal 5 SP (2 times per turn)\n- If this unit's SP is at max, gain 1 [HitDamageUp] next turn when this unit heals SP with this effect (once per turn)",
